title: Marvel Milestones (2005) #9
description:
From the Mighty Marvel Digital Archives come two rare tales from the early Ultimate Universe! Danny Rand – the Hero-for-Hire known as Iron Fist – makes his Ultimate debut in ULTIMATE SPIDER-MAN #1/2, and Quicksilver and the Scarlet Witch come to grips with Magneto’s seeming death in the never-before-reprinted ULTIMATE X-MEN #1/2! Plus: Thrill to the Golden Age adventures of Microman and Mantor the Magician from HUMAN TORCH #2 (Fall 1940)!
48 PGS./T+ SUGGESTED FOR TEENS AND UP ...$3.99
